OL,3,CSecurity stepped up as England and
OL,4,CArgentina fans prepare for World Cup
OL,5,Cshowdown
OL,7,FPolice have stepped up security across
OL,8,FAtlanta as the city prepares to host
OL,9,FEngland's World Cup semi-final against
OL,10,FArgentina ` a fixture fans have said
OL,11,Fhas "so much history and so much
OL,12,Frivalry".
OL,14,FThe Atlanta Police Department said
OL,15,Fextra officers and resources had
OL,16,Falready been deployed around the city
OL,17,Fbefore Wednesday's match, with
OL,18,Fincreased patrols planned around the
OL,19,FMercedes-Benz Stadium as well as
OL,20,F"entertainment districts and other
OL,21,Fhigh-traffic areas".
OL,26,@sD@EOUtD@HO]|D@AOU}D@SO]
