OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1784081890
OL,3,CSecurity stepped up as England and
OL,4,CArgentina fans prepare for World Cup
OL,5,Cshowdown
OL,7,FThe move comes as thousands of England
OL,8,Fand Argentina supporters are set to
OL,9,Fdescend on the city for the first
OL,10,FWorld Cup knockout meeting between the
OL,11,Fnations since David Beckham's red card
OL,12,Fin England's dramatic last-16 exit in
OL,13,F1998.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
