OL,3,CSecurity stepped up as England and
OL,4,CArgentina fans prepare for World Cup
OL,5,Cshowdown
OL,7,FA statement from the Atlanta Police
OL,8,FDepartment said: "As Atlanta prepares
OL,9,Fto host an upcoming FIFA World Cup
OL,10,Fsemi-final match and welcomes
OL,11,Fincreased numbers of residents and
OL,12,Fvisitors, the Atlanta Police
OL,13,FDepartment has enhanced its citywide
OL,14,Fpublic safety and security posture.
OL,26,@pD@ROU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,320,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31904
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1784081890
OL,3,CSecurity stepped up as England and
OL,4,CArgentina fans prepare for World Cup
OL,5,Cshowdown
OL,7,F"Additional personnel and resources
OL,8,Fare already deployed and will continue
OL,9,Fto be strategically assigned in and
OL,10,Faround the event venues, entertainment
OL,11,Fdistricts and other high-traffic areas
OL,12,Fto help ensure a safe and enjoyable
OL,13,Fexperience for everyone.
OL,15,F"These proactive measures are designed
OL,16,Fto protect the public, deter criminal
OL,17,Factivity and ensure residents and
OL,18,Fvisitors can safely enjoy this
OL,19,Fhistoric event."
OL,26,@oD@AOUwD@AOU{D@PO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/12
