OL,3,CSecurity stepped up as England and
OL,4,CArgentina fans prepare for World Cup
OL,5,Cshowdown
OL,7,FEngland supporter Rob Osborn said the
OL,8,Ffixture still carried the weight of
OL,9,Fdecades of history, including Diego
OL,10,FMaradona's "Hand of God" goal at the
OL,11,F1986 World Cup.
OL,13,FSpeaking in Atlanta on Monday, the fan
OL,14,Ffrom Stoke Golding, Leicestershire,
OL,15,Ftold the PA news agency: "Yeah,
OL,16,Fthere's so much history and so much
OL,17,Frivalry ` going back to 1986.
OL,26,@rD@LOUrD@XO]wD@ZOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,320,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31906
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1784081890
OL,3,CSecurity stepped up as England and
OL,4,CArgentina fans prepare for World Cup
OL,5,Cshowdown
OL,7,F"If we can stop the Argentinians from
OL,8,Fcheating, like they have done in this
OL,9,Ftournament again, but with the hand of
OL,10,FFIFA, then I think we might have a
OL,11,Fshot.
OL,13,F"I think we've got to have luck on our
OL,14,Fside, but we'll see. We'll see how it
OL,15,Fgoes."
OL,17,FAsked whether victory would finally
OL,18,Flay some of the rivalry to rest, he
OL,19,Fsaid: "It will close the book on it,
OL,20,Fwon't it?
OL,26,@oD@AOUuD@AOUwD@FO]{D@GOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/12
