OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1784081890
OL,3,CSecurity stepped up as England and
OL,4,CArgentina fans prepare for World Cup
OL,5,Cshowdown
OL,7,F"The Azteca, we weren't there, but it
OL,8,Fwould have been amazing to experience
OL,9,Fthat.
OL,11,F"If the guys can get us over the line
OL,12,Fof ticking that box and closing the
OL,13,Fmouths, then it's that voodoo being
OL,14,Fput to bed."
OL,16,FAhead of the semi final, the police
OL,17,Fofficer responsible for the UK's
OL,18,Ffootball policing said England
OL,19,Fsupporters had set an example
OL,20,Fthroughout the tournament.
OL,26,@oD@AOUsD@AOUvD@LO]
