OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1784081890
OL,3,CSecurity stepped up as England and
OL,4,CArgentina fans prepare for World Cup
OL,5,Cshowdown
OL,7,FChief Constable Mark Roberts of
OL,8,FCheshire Police, the UK's football
OL,9,Fpolicing lead, said the conduct of
OL,10,FEngland fans at Saturday's quarter-
OL,11,Ffinal victory over Norway in Miami had
OL,12,Fagain been "exemplary", with "no
OL,13,Fanimosity between fans at the end of
OL,14,Fthe match".
OL,26,@tD@LOUtD@VO]tD@^OUvD@JO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/12
