PN,31909
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1784081890
OL,3,CSecurity stepped up as England and
OL,4,CArgentina fans prepare for World Cup
OL,5,Cshowdown
OL,7,FHe contrasted that with more than 500
OL,8,Freported incidents and more than 100
OL,9,Farrests across the UK during the same
OL,10,Fevening, most of them alcohol-related,
OL,11,Fand urged supporters watching
OL,12,FWednesday's match at home to follow
OL,13,Fthe example set by fans travelling in
OL,14,Fthe United States.
OL,16,FEngland goalkeeper Jordan Pickford
OL,17,Falso said his side would not allow
OL,18,Fthemselves to become distracted by the
OL,19,Femotion surrounding the fixture.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
