PN,31910
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1784081890
OL,3,CSecurity stepped up as England and
OL,4,CArgentina fans prepare for World Cup
OL,5,Cshowdown
OL,7,F"I think you've seen throughout the
OL,8,Ftournament our desire to win tackles,
OL,9,Fwe've not got into any scuffles or
OL,10,Fanything," he said.
OL,12,F"We've been very well respected within
OL,13,Fthe game. Decisions go our way, they
OL,14,Fdon't go our way, we just reset, we go
OL,15,Fagain and we let the football do the
OL,16,Ftalking."
OL,18,FPickford said England's focus was
OL,19,Fsimply on earning a place in the World
OL,20,FCup final rather than dwelling on the
OL,21,Fhistory between the countries.
OL,26,@oD@AOUrD@JO]tD@AOUxD@IO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/12
