OL,3,CSecurity stepped up as England and
OL,4,CArgentina fans prepare for World Cup
OL,5,Cshowdown
OL,7,FHe said: "It's us against them to get
OL,8,Fa place in the final, and it's a game
OL,9,Fof football. Ninety minutes, 120,
OL,10,Fpenalties.
OL,12,F"We're ready for anything, and it's us
OL,13,Fagainst them and it's about who comes
OL,14,Fout on top."
OL,26,@oD@JOUtD@AOUvD@LO]
