OL,3,CSecurity stepped up as England and
OL,4,CArgentina fans prepare for World Cup
OL,5,Cshowdown
OL,7,FThe match also comes against the
OL,8,Fbackdrop of renewed political tension
OL,9,Fover the Falkland Islands after
OL,10,FDowning Street rejected claims by
OL,11,FArgentina's foreign minister that the
OL,12,Fislanders were an "artificially
OL,13,Fimplanted" population.
OL,15,FDowning Street insisted the islanders
OL,16,Fare British and have the right to
OL,17,Fdetermine their own future, with Sir
OL,18,FKeir Starmer's spokesman saying
OL,19,Ffootball "should be about the game and
OL,20,Fabout bringing people together".
